The transport was flying high, and it finally saw the island far below.

The nameless commander was going to enjoy the fight. Minions...
finally worthy adversaries! But they first had to get down there.

???: Atlantis, this is Governmental Transport Aegis approaching for
immediate reinforcements. We need access to a secure landing place as
well as full intelligence regarding the battle.
